# UI Design System

**Source of truth:** `src/App.jsx` (lines 11тАУ28 for tokens/primitives; screen patterns in `Home`, `Roster`, etc.)

Full catalog: `docs/design/ui-reference.md`  
Application docs: `docs/prototype/README.md`

## Before building UI

1. Read existing primitives and color tokens in `src/App.jsx` (`C`, `ff`, `fd`, `Hero`, `Cd`, `Btn`, тАж).
2. Reuse them тАФ do not invent parallel button/card/color systems.
3. Match layout: mobile-first, `maxWidth: 430`, horizontal padding `20px`, bottom safe area `110px` for tab bar.

## Color tokens (`C`)

| Token | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `bg`, `sf`, `cd`, `el` | Background layers (app тЖТ surface тЖТ card тЖТ elevated) |
| `ink`, `sub`, `dim` | Primary, secondary, muted text |
| `ln` | Borders and dividers |
| `br`, `br2`, `brG`, `brS` | Brand orange (primary actions, active tab) |
| `gn`, `gnS`, `gT` | Success / positive |
| `bl`, `blS` | Info / links |
| `vi`, `viS` | AI features |
| `am`, `amS` | Warning / drip / locked |
| `ro`, `roS` | Error / injury / loss |

Never hardcode hex colors that duplicate these tokens.

## Typography

- **Body / UI:** `ff` тЖТ DM Sans (`@fontsource/dm-sans` in `main.jsx`)
- **Headings / stats:** `fd` тЖТ Nunito (`@fontsource/nunito`)
- Screen titles on `Hero`: Nunito 28px/800, white + text shadow
- Section headers: `SH` component or `fd` 18px/800 `C.ink`

## Primitives тАФ use these, don't recreate

| Component | When to use |
|-----------|-------------|
| `Hero` | Screen header with image + gradient |
| `Strip` | Section divider banner |
| `Cd` | Card container (`tap` for pressable rows) |
| `Btn` | Actions (`primary` = orange gradient) |
| `Pill` | Status / position badges |
| `Av` / `IA` | Avatars |
| `SH` | Section title + optional "View All" |
| `PB` | Labeled progress bar |
| `Rg` | Donut percentage gauge |
| `Sp` | Sparkline chart |
| `Bk` | Back navigation |
| `I` | Icons (30+ names in dictionary) |

## Patterns

- Screen mount: `animation: "fu .3s ease"` on root container
- Primary CTA: `<Btn primary full>` with optional `<I n="..." />`
- List rows: `<Cd tap={...} sx={{ display:"flex", minHeight:64|72, ... }}>`
- Filter chips: pill buttons with `background: selected ? C.br : C.cd`
- Inputs: `background: C.cd`, `border: 1px solid C.ln`, `borderRadius: 14`, `fontFamily: ff`
- Touch targets: `minHeight: 44` minimum

## Do not

- Add Tailwind, MUI, shadcn, or other UI libraries without an explicit story requirement
- Use colors from `index.css` / `App.css` (Vite boilerplate тАФ not the app theme)
- Create new one-off `<button>` or card styles when `Btn` / `Cd` suffice

## Extraction (when refactoring)

When a story grows beyond `App.jsx`, extract to `src/ui/` or `src/components/ui/` **by moving existing primitives unchanged** тАФ tokens (`C`, `ff`, `fd`) first, then components. Update imports; do not redesign during extraction.
